      "target": {
        "kind": "pull_request",
        "title": "feat(tools): add configurable tool confirmation gate",
        "body": "## Summary\n\n- Add disabled-by-default `tools.confirmation` config for tool-level confirmation policy.\n- Add deterministic tool risk classification with `none`, `auto`, and `always` tiers.\n- Add assistant-text-aware auto confirmation detection before risky tool execution.\n- Preserve transcript/tool-result shape when a tool is skipped for confirmation.\n\nRefs #23451\n\n## Behavior\n\nWhen enabled, OpenClaw can now block risky same-response tool calls before execution if the assistant text asks the user for confirmation.\n\nExample protected case:\n\n```text\nAssistant text: \"Should I delete this?\"\nTool call: edit/write/exec\nResult: tool is skipped and a blocked tool result is recorded\n```\n\n## Compatibility\n\n- Disabled by default.\n- Existing tool behavior is unchanged unless `tools.confirmation.enabled=true`.\n- Existing plugin `before_tool_call` approval behavior remains intact.\n\n## Stacking\n\nThis PR is stacked on #85341 (internalize agent runtime). It should be reviewed/merged after that PR lands, or rebased on main once #85341 is merged.\n\n## Verification\n\n```bash\nnode scripts/run-vitest.mjs src/agents/agent-tool-confirmation.test.ts\nnode scripts/run-vitest.mjs src/agents/runtime/agent-loop.tool-confirmation.test.ts\nnode scripts/run-vitest.mjs src/config/schema.test.ts src/config/schema.help.quality.test.ts\nnode scripts/run-vitest.mjs src/agents/agent-tools.before-tool-call.e2e.test.ts src/plugins/hooks.before-tool-call.test.ts src/gateway/server-methods/plugin-approval.test.ts src/gateway/method-scopes.test.ts\nnode scripts/run-vitest.mjs src/agents/embedded-agent-runner/run.incomplete-turn.test.ts\nnode scripts/run-tsgo.mjs -b tsconfig.projects.json\npnpm exec oxfmt --check --threads=1 <changed files>\ngit diff --check\n```\n\n## Real behavior proof\n\n**Behavior addressed:**\nSame-response assistant confirmation text no longer allows a risky tool to execute before the user can respond when `tools.confirmation.enabled=true`.\n\n**Environment:**\nLocal OpenClaw checkout on branch `fix/tool-confirmation-gate`, Linux, Node, pnpm.\n\n**Steps:**\nConfigured `tools.confirmation.enabled=true`, ran a local temp-file edit scenario.\n\n**Evidence:**\nAssistant response contained confirmation text, tool result returned `status=blocked` `deniedReason=tool-confirmation`, temp file remained unchanged.\n\n**Observed result:**\nRisky tool was skipped before execution.\n\n**Not tested:**\nLive approval UX in every chat channel.",
        "branch": "fix/tool-confirmation-gate",
